729853f-a.title: Richmond: Victory Boulevard - Manor Road
729853f-a.text:
Victory Boulevard, at the N.W. corner of Manor Road. This house
belonged to Thos. W. Eagleson, in 1898; to Agnea A. Arden, in 1907;
and to J.M. Hoffman, in 1917.
May 6, 1929
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
